---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: CID Parker Colorado Basement Finishing and Remodeling
bodyClass: "ant-one-sidebar ant-sidebar-second path-frontpage"
permalink: /index.html
---

{# Hero image + Intro overlay #}
<div class="hero-wrapper">
  <div class="hero-image">
    <img loading="eager"
      src="{{ site.heroImage.src }}"
      alt="{{ site.heroImage.alt }}"
      width="1280"
      height="450" />
  </div>
  <div class="home-intro" id="block-basementfinishingremodeling">
    <h2>Basement Finishing &amp; Remodeling</h2>
    <div class="home-intro-content">
      <p>CID Basements offers complete design and construction services to finish your basement or any remodeling project in your home. We specialize in unique floor plans, room design, custom cabinetry, and architectural details with personalized service and attention to detail. We offer a full range of services including:</p>
      <div class="services-list">
        <span>Basement Finishing</span>
        <span>Home Repair</span>
        <span>Basement Remodeling</span>
        <span>Roof Replacement</span>
      </div>
      <a class="btn" href="/basement-content/basement-finishing-and-remodeling-services/">Our Services</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/contact/">Free Estimate</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{# Main content + sidebar #}
<div class="page-layout has-sidebar">
  <main role="main" id="main-content">

    <div class="home-blocks-grid">
      <div class="home-block" id="block-projects">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <p>Please have a look at some of our past projects and begin imagining what CID ltd. can do to "take your basement to a new level" From custom wet bars, entertainment centers and custom office suites, CID basements can design and inspire a truly one of a kind project for you.</p>
        <a class="btn" href="/projects/">View Projects</a>
      </div>

      <div class="home-block" id="block-blog">
        <h2>Handyman Blog</h2>
        {% set latestPost = collections.blog | first %}
        {% if latestPost %}
          <p>{{ latestPost.data.description }}</p>
          <a class="read-full-post" href="{{ latestPost.url }}">read full post</a>
        {% endif %}
        <a class="btn" href="/blog/">More Posts</a>
      </div>

      <div class="home-block" id="block-testimonials">
        <h2>Testimonials</h2>
        {% set firstTestimonial = collections.testimonials | first %}
        {% if firstTestimonial %}
          {{ firstTestimonial.templateContent | safe }}
        {% endif %}
        <a class="btn" href="/testimonials/">Customer feedback</a>
      </div>

      <div class="home-block" id="block-freeconsult">
        <h2>Free Consult</h2>
        <p>We can help you create the perfect space for you to enjoy in your home. Contact us today and we will help you turn your dream into a reality from start to finish. Give us a call at {{ site.phone }} to get started. What do you have in mind for basement finishing or home renovations? Together we can make it happen!</p>
        <a class="btn" href="/contact/">Get an estimate</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>

  <aside class="layout-sidebar-second" role="complementary">
    {% include "components/sidebar.njk" %}
  </aside>
</div>
